00:02:07.922 --> 00:02:09.694
bio vrlo koristan,

00:02:09.694 --> 00:02:11.382
proširio se čitavim svijetom.

00:02:11.382 --> 00:02:13.851
I danas, svaka zemlja

00:02:13.851 --> 00:02:15.465
izrađuje BDP statistike.

00:02:17.185 --> 00:02:19.922
